About JSFring

Full web application who integrated all Java EE frameworks: Spring, JPA, JSF, AngularJS, ...

Project Modules

This project has declared the following modules:

Name Description
Common Common dependencies for other modules

Model Model layer: SQL & NoSQL

Webservice Webservice application
